      ** Other parms
      ** Positions Combined Indicator,
     C                   PARM                    DDPCIN
 
      ** Outputs
      ** Error fields/message IDs/message data (arrays) from/to caller
     C                   PARM                    FldNamXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgIDXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgDtaXAr
